### Cadastrar usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Misael",
  "email": "misael@email.com",
  "senha": "12345678",
  "telefone": "(74)99999-9999",
  "cidade": "Irecê"
}

